                .subtitle.subtitle_center
                    | Everyone's reasons for learning user interface design are different. If you're already a developer,or a PM, or a UX designer, why develop this totally separate skill?
                .row
                    -
                        var prices = [
                        {
                            title: 'Basic',
                            price: '12.0',
                            arrOptions: ['One User', 'Multiple Access', 'SMS Support', '24/7 Online Support']
                        },
                        {
                            title: 'Standard',
                            price: '24.0',
                            arrOptions: ['Five Users', 'Multiple Access', 'SMS Support', '24/7 Online Support']
                        },
                        {
                            title: 'Premium',
